computedFields.name: Filter_Renewal_RecordType
computedFields.saqlExpression: case when 'RecordType.Name' == "Renewal/Attrition" or 'RecordType.Name' == "Renewal/Attrition - LOCKED" then "Renewal" when 'RecordType.Name' == "Renewal/Attrition" or 'RecordType.Name' == "Renewal/Attrition - LOCKED" or 'RecordType.Name' == "MC Services Renewal/Attrition" or 'RecordType.Name' == "MC Services Renewal/Attrition - LOCKED" then "Marketing" else "False" end

computedFields.name: Filter_Renewal_Role
computedFields.saqlExpression: case when 'Owner.Role.Name' matches "CFL - RENEWALS" then "True" else "False" end

computedFields.name: Filter_Renewal_Role_Mkt_Pdt
computedFields.saqlExpression: case when 'Owner.Role.Name' matches "MC - CFL - RENEWALS" or 'Owner.Name' == "Hollie Suffield" or 'Owner.Name' == "Melissa Barlow" or 'Owner.Name' == "Leah Ring" or 'Owner.Name' == "Gwynne Morris" then "Marketing" when 'Owner.Role.Name' matches "PDT" then "Pardot" else "Other" end

computedFields.name: Filter_OppName
computedFields.saqlExpression: case when ('Name' matches "Off Cycle Forecasting" or 'Name' matches "OffCycle Forecasting") then "Off Cycle" when 'Name' matches "R6" then "Radian6" when 'Name' matches "Radian6" then "Radian6" when 'Name' matches "buybuddy" then "Buddy Media" when 'Name' matches "buy buddy" then "Buddy Media" when 'Name' matches "buddy media" then "Buddy Media" else "True" end

computedFields.name: Filter_AccName
computedFields.saqlExpression: case when ('Account.Name' matches "Off Cycle Forecasting" or 'Account.Name' matches "OffCycle Forecasting") then "Off Cycle" else "True" end

computedFields.name: Filter_Type
computedFields.saqlExpression: case when 'Type' matches "Out Clause" then "Out Clause" when 'Type' matches "Price Increase" then "Price Increase" when'Type' matches "Off-Cycle" then "Off-Cycle" else "On-Cycle" end

computedFields.name: Filter_Records
computedFields.saqlExpression: case when 'Filter_Renewal_RecordType' == "Renewal" and 'Filter_Renewal_Role' == "True" and 'Filter_Renewal_Role_Mkt_Pdt' == "Other" and 'Filter_OppName' == "True" and 'Filter_AccName' == "True"and ( 'Filter_Type' == "On-Cycle" or 'Filter_Type' == "Off-Cycle") then "Renewals" when ('Filter_Renewal_RecordType' == "Marketing" or 'Filter_Renewal_RecordType' == "Renewal") and 'Filter_Renewal_Role_Mkt_Pdt' == "Marketing" and 'Filter_OppName' != "Buddy Media" and 'Account.Non_Profit_Account__c' == "false" and 'Type' != "Off-Cycle Non Coterminous Order" then "Marketing" else "All" end

computedFields.name: Metric_Type
computedFields.saqlExpression: case when 'Type' in ["BTA","Envision","Marketing Architect","Program Architect","Springboard (XD)"] then "Architects (PA, BA)" when 'Type' in ["Expeditions"] then "Expeditions" when 'Type' in ["Implementation Architect"] then "Imp Architect" when 'Type' in ["Proactive Monitoring","TAM"] then "TAM / Proactive Monitoring" when 'Type' in ["Services Projects"] then "Core Projects" when 'Type' in ["Marketing Cloud Projects"] then "MC Projects" when 'Type' in ["Marketing Cloud Programs"] then "MC@" when 'Type' in ["Commerce Cloud - Services Project","Strategic Project (CC only)"] then "CC Strategic Projects" end
computedFields.label: Metric_Type

computedFields.name: Products_Projects
computedFields.saqlExpression: case when 'Type' in ["BTA","Envision","Marketing Architect","Program Architect","Springboard (XD)","Lightning Boost","Expeditions","Implementation Architect","Proactive Monitoring","TAM"] then "Products"  when 'Type' in ["Marketing Cloud Projects","Services Projects","Marketing Cloud Programs","Commerce Cloud - Services Project","Strategic Project (CC only)"] then "Projects" end
computedFields.label: Products_Projects

computedFields.name: Region
computedFields.saqlExpression: case when 'pse__Region__c' in ["AMER Retail + CPG"] then "AMER B2C"  when 'pse__Region__c' in ["AMER Key East","AMER Key West","AMER Key Select Canada PubSec","Canada"] then "AMER Key+" when 'pse__Region__c' in ["Salesforce.org (Foundation)"] then "Salesforce.org" when 'pse__Region__c' in ["AMER SELGEN CMRCL","AMER Mid CMRCL","AMER CMRCL & SMB"] then "AMER CMRCL + SMB" when 'pse__Region__c' in ["LACA","LACA Brazil","LACA CAS"] then "LACA" end

computedFields.saqlExpression: case when 'PricebookEntryId.Product2Id.sfbase__Recurring__c' == "true" then 'sfbase__MonthlyUnitPrice__c' * 'Quantity' * 12  else 'sfbase__MonthlyUnitPrice__c' * 'Quantity' end
